ufacturing services in addition the company provides replacement parts fleet management solutions diagnostic tools training and other services to commercial vehicle aftermarket distributors service partners and fleet operators it also serves truck and bus original equipment manufacturers oems trailer oems and car manufacturers wabco holdings inc was founded in  and is headquartered in brussels belgium detailed description chaussee de la hulpe brussels  belgiumfounded in  employees phone      fax      wwwwabcoautocom key executives for wabco holdings inc mr jacques h g esculier chairman of the board of directors and chief executive officer age  total annual compensation m mr prashanth mahendrarajah chief financial officer age  total annual compensation k mr nick rens president of trailer systems aftermarket  offhighway age  total annual compensation k mr jorge solis presidenttruck bus  car original equipment manufacturers  vpvehicle dynamics controls business age  total annual compensation k mr nicolas bardot chief supply chain officer age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  wabco holdings inc key developments zf friedrichshafen and wabco reportedly in merger talks jul   zf friedrichshafen ag recently held advanced takeover talks with wabco holdings inc nysewbc before they fell apart amid resistance from zf’s board wabco disclosed when it reported secondquarter earnings last week that it had received a takeover offer from an unnamed party according to people familiar with the matter zf is the mystery bidder it isn’t clear whether zf could return with another bid and according to people familiar with the matter it’s possible wabco could draw another suitor wabco holdings inc announces unaudited consolidated earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended june   revises earnings guidance for full year  jul   wabco holdings inc announced unaudited consolidated earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended june   for t